## File Naming Conventions

- Models: `User.swift`, `Message.swift` (singular, PascalCase)
- Views: `LoginView.swift`, `ChatView.swift` (descriptive + View suffix)
- ViewModels: `AuthViewModel.swift`, `ChatViewModel.swift` (descriptive + ViewModel suffix)
- Repositories: `UserRepository.swift` (singular + Repository suffix)
- Services: `AuthenticationService.swift` (descriptive + Service suffix)
- Extensions: `Date+Extensions.swift` (Type + Extensions)
- Constants: `AppConstants.swift`, `FirebaseConstants.swift` (descriptive + Constants)

